<h2>🔐 Two-factor authentication</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>
<p>Enter the 6-digit verification code below to complete your login:</p>

<div class="code-block">
  <div class="label">2FA verification code</div>
  <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
</div>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>⚠️ Security note:</strong> this code expires in <strong>5 minutes</strong>.</p>
  <p style="margin-top: 6px; font-size: 13px;">
    Didn't request this? Ignore this email and consider securing your account.
  </p>
</div>
